# YAML 1.1

# Nombre del paquete (minúsculas-separado-con-guiones)
name: siga-client

# Autor
author: Oficina de Software Libre de la Universidad de La Laguna <bardinux@osl.ull.es>

# Priority
priority: extra

# Section
section: net

# Descripción corta
shortdesc: "Dummy package that installs the configuration for a SIGA Client"

# Descipción larga, las lineas han de estar separadas por "\n "
longdesc: "This package is only for a client of a SIGA Classroom. \n WANING: Don't install this at your home. \n It will crash your installation."

# Versión del paquete
version: 3.1.3

# Cambios en esta versión
changes:
    - Updated long description.
    - Fixed bug setting permissions in mountpoints.
    - Deleted version of cifs-utils dependency.
    - Revert server="dummy" in pam_mount.conf.xml
    - Replaced allowed IPs by subnet range in ufw rules.
    - Added rsize=61440 option to mount.cifs to workaround Debian bug 803941
    - Fix problem detecting mountpoint in PDI/PAS accounts.
